Live at the Regal is a live recording of legendary blues guitarist and vocalist B.B. King. The album was recorded November 21, 1964 and is considered one of the greatest blues albums ever recorded. Live at the Regal was selected by the Library of Congress in 2005 for permanent preservation in the National Recording Registry
